subject: Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: Ryan Callahan’s breakaway goal with just 20 seconds remaining gave the Rangers a dramatic 4-3 victory over Metallurg Magnitogorsk to win the inaugural Victoria Cup on Wednesday.
snippet: Ryan Callahan’s breakaway goal with just 20 seconds remaining gave the Rangers a dramatic 4-3 victory over Metallurg Magnitogorsk to win the inaugural Victoria Cup on Wednesday.
